OL,3,COne in 23 Guernsey residents waiting
OL,4,Cfor inpatient appointments
OL,6,FOne in 23 residents are waiting for
OL,7,Finpatient appointments, a new Health
OL,8,Fand Social Care (HSC) report has found.
OL,10,FThousands more patients were cared for
OL,11,Fby secondary healthcare services
OL,12,Fduring 2023 compared to the previous
OL,13,Fyear but wait times are below target,
OL,14,Fwith the longest lists for
OL,15,Fgastroenterology and orthopaedics.
OL,17,FGuernsey's Medical Director Dr Peter
OL,18,FRabey said: "We still have large
OL,19,Fnumbers on waiting lists in those two
OL,20,Fspecialities and we've been focusing
OL,21,Freally hard to reduce them.
