OL,6,F"In gastroenterology, we got a
OL,7,Fvisiting team to do over 500 patients
OL,8,Flast year and we took over 1000
OL,9,Fpatients off the waiting list last
OL,10,Fyear in total."
OL,12,FOrthopaedics also saw a 22% reduction
OL,13,Fin cancelled operations following the
OL,14,Fopening of the dedicated De Havilland
OL,15,FWard at the end of 2022.
OL,17,FOverall, more than 2,800 islanders are
OL,18,Fwaiting for inpatient appointments.
